      <title>Ares 寻求与房地产投资者 GLP Capital Partners 达成交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/ares-said-to-explore-deal-for-real-estate-investor-glp-capital-partners</link>
